short_description:
A big update is coming...
MySurf is a unique web browser that you can customize yourself!  It is unique because you can customize the color of the browser and more coming soon!
Features:
1. You can customize the color of the browser.
2. You can set a password that you need to enter to use the application.
3. You can change the homepage.
4. You can change the search engine.
5. Have links to many popular websites in the menu bar.
6. Built-in update system to check for updates and get more features.
7. Super fast browsing!
8. Contact us is built-in.
9. Print the webpage you are on right from the browser.
10. Bookmarks!
Many more features coming soon!
summary: MySurf is a unique web browser that you can customize yourself!
